    "body": "```\nformat = \"\"\"\n[](color_orange)\\\n$os\\\n[](bg:color_yellow fg:color_orange)\\\n$directory\\\n[](fg:color_yellow bg:color_aqua)\\\n$git_branch\\\n$git_status\\\n$git_commit\\\n[](fg:color_aqua bg:color_blue)\\\n$nodejs\\\n[](fg:color_blue bg:color_bg3)\\\n[](fg:color_bg3 bg:color_bg1)\\\n$time\\\n[ ](fg:color_bg1)\\\n$line_break\\\n$battery\\\n$cmd_duration\\\n$character\"\"\"\n```\n\n```\n[git_commit]\ntag_disabled = false\ntag_symbol = \"🔖 \"\nformat = '[[ $hash$tag ](fg:color_fg0 bg:color_aqua)]($style)'\n```",
