    "body": "Resolved.\n\n`only_detached` is `true` by default.\n```\n[git_commit]\nonly_detached = false\ntag_disabled = false\ntag_symbol = \"🔖 \"\nformat = '[[ $hash$tag ](fg:color_fg0 bg:color_aqua)]($style)'\n```\n\nNow I see hash and tag.",
